---
title: Carb Smart Cumin-Spiced Shrimp with Roasted Veggies
description: Mexican flavours star in this vibrant dish. Cumin-spiced shrimp are pan-seared and served over a colourful bed of squash, red bell pepper and cabbage — all topped with feta cheese. A drizzle of creamy avocado aioli lends the dish herbaceous flavours, while toasted pepitas add a subtle crunch throughout.

